ZH: 春天来了，桃花绽放了。
EN: Spring is here, and the peach blossoms are blooming.

ZH: 春风吹过，粉色的桃花簇拥着整个山谷。
EN: The spring breeze blows, and the pink peach blossoms cover the whole valley.

ZH: 看！那些桃花儿，就像一朵朵红云在树上。
EN: Look! Those peach blossoms are like red clouds on the trees.

ZH: 桃花开了，表示冬天已经过去，春天来临了。
EN: When the peach blossoms bloom, it indicates that winter is over and spring has come.

ZH: 这座园子里的桃花每年都特别美。
EN: The peach blossoms in this garden are particularly beautiful every year.

ZH: 这片桃花海在每年春天都吸引了很多游客。
EN: This peach blossom sea attracts many tourists every spring.

ZH: 沿着这条小路走，你会看到一片桃花林。
EN: Follow this path, and you will see a peach blossom forest.

ZH: 小明拿着相机，准备去拍摄桃花的美景。
EN: Xiaoming is holding a camera, ready to capture the beauty of the peach blossoms.

ZH: 桃花纷飞的时候，我总是感到心情愉快。
EN: I always feel happy when the peach blossoms are flying.

ZH: 今年的桃花开得特别早。
EN: The peach blossoms bloomed particularly early this year.

ZH: 桃花盛开的时候，整个村子都被粉红的颜色所覆盖。
EN: When the peach blossoms are in full bloom, the entire village is covered in pink.

ZH: 弯下腰，你能闻到桃花的淡淡香味。
EN: Bend down, and you can smell the faint fragrance of the peach blossoms.

ZH: 她穿着一袭粉色的裙子，站在桃花树下，仿佛是一个仙女。
EN: She wears a pink dress and stands under the peach blossom tree, like a fairy.

ZH: 爷爷经常带我去他种的园子里看桃花。
EN: Grandpa often takes me to see the peach blossoms in his garden.

ZH: 夜晚的桃花树下，月光映照着银色的花瓣。
EN: Under the peach blossom tree at night, the moonlight reflects off the silver petals.

ZH: 桃花的开放让我们充满了希望和新的开始。
EN: The blooming of peach blossoms fills us with hope and new beginnings.

ZH: 他在诗中写道：“春风吹过，桃花红梅白，谁在花树下，谁又伴我眠。”
EN: He wrote in his poem, "The spring breeze blows, pink peach blossoms, white plum blossoms, who is under the tree, who accompanies me to sleep."

ZH: 这幅画里的桃花看起来栩栩如生。
EN: The peach blossoms in this painting look lifelike.

ZH: 我们在桃花树下野餐，度过了一个美好的下午。
EN: We had a wonderful afternoon having a picnic under the peach tree.

ZH: 那个村庄被桃花的美景装点得如同童话般的仙境。
EN: The village is decorated with the picturesque beauty of the peach blossoms, like a fairyland from a fairy tale.
